(** * Derived Operation <<foldmapd>> *)
(**********************************************************************)
Definition foldMapd {T: Type -> Type} `{Mapdt E T}
  `{op: Monoid_op M} `{unit: Monoid_unit M}
  {A: Type} (f: E * A -> M): T A -> M :=
  mapdt (G := const M) (B := False) f.
